{"id": "aos003", "name": "Audio_ARC_H_694_5_20", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Hmm... ugh...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "What's wrong? Is it too difficult? Maybe you should take a break?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "I'm fine... Let me finish this set...\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "You've been in bed for nine months. It's natural that your muscles feel weak... Fortunately, you can recover from that with just rehabilitation.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Yes... Whew... Done...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Here, have a drink.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Thank you...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Do you remember this? It's the triple juice. This used to be your favorite beverage.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "You don't remember...? It's okay. The fact that you were able to wake up from your coma is already more than I could ask for...\nAh, right! Here, your Tuner-san.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_boot", "Tuner-san ON"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "My...?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Aroma, Good morning~ Good morning~</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "It's an electronic pet that has been with you since you were little. It contains so many past photos and videos of us. Let's take a look. Maybe it'll help you recover your memory.\nTuner-san, play Album 6860420\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Album 6860420, projection start.</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_3", "Song（Night Keepers - Bring the light）"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>*Every time we hide  \nInto shadow that can make us feel love \nEat the sorrow drink a cup of fear*</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>Sister! Happy birthday!</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "This is...?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "You were celebrating my birthday with me. Remember? Aroma's singing really is beautiful...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... I don't remember anything... but this song sounds very familiar.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>Hahaha! Sis, you look so funny!</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>How dare you throw a cake at me! You little... No running! I'll get you too! Hahaha!</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<i>*Chuckles*</i>... It looks like so much fun.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "You were one heck of a mischievous brat; who knew you would become so shy after you grow up. \nSo, how was it? Did anything ring a bell?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... No... I'm sorry.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Ah... B, But if the things I forgot are all happy memories like that one, I really hope I can remember them soon... sister.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...... Aroma...... <i>*Sobs*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ah... no good, no good. How can I act so depressed like that? You're right; we need to help you recover your memory soon. \nYour body is recovering quite well physically. I can apply to the Academy for you to resume your studies. You have a lot of good friends in class. Staying together with them will certainly help with your conditions.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "The Academy...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Although you've been absent for more than one semester, as long as you pass the continuation exam, you can stay in your original class. Aroma was a top student; you can definitely do it!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Hmm...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "How did it go? Is she feeling alright?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ah, even though you've met him before; do you remember him? Your sister's husband Noah.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "No... I don't remember.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Oh, how unfortunate, Mr. \"forgotten savior\".\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Haha... I don't mind.\nAroma, I'm Noah; I'm your sister's husband. I'm also currently your attending physician. We live in the same apartment. If you have any problems, feel free to rely on me.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Got it... Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Don't be fooled by his demeanor... He's the least reliable person in this household.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Haha......\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "That's mean... Here, Aroma; put this on.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "These three suspending devices are stabilizers. You are required to wear them 24/7. Since you are still recovering from surgery, you may experience phantom nausea or dizziness, even hallucinations at times. These devices can help suppress those symptoms.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Of course, these aftereffects are all temporary, just like your memory loss. The operation was a huge success and your brain is now in great condition. Therefore, these symptoms will gradually disappear as time goes on. Your memory will gradually recover as well. When that time comes, we can live happily together again, like how we used to.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Yes...\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "These devices also have the function to monitor brainwaves. If they detect anything abnormal, they will instantly contact us via a built-in application. If you feel any discomfort or encounter any other problem, just press this button. By doing so, we'll be able to know your situation and location right away.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, if you have any problems, please tell us. We are all here by your side.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Understood. Thank you so much.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "It's the least we can do.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "う……あ……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "どうしたの？苦しい？\nちょっと休憩にしましょう。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "いいの……これだけやっちゃう……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "9か月も寝たきりだったから、筋肉が衰えているのね……\nリハビリだけで何とかなりそうでよかったわ。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん……ふぅ……終わった……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "おいで。水分を取りなさい。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "ありがとう……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "覚えてる？このジュース、前はとても好きだったのよ。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "思い出せない……？\nいいのよ。お姉ちゃんは、あなたが目を覚ましてくれただけで充分だから。\nあ！そうだ！ほら。あなたのチューナー君。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_boot", "チューナー君ON"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "私の……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>Aroma オハヨウ！オハヨウ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "小さいころからずっと一緒にいる電子ペットよ。\n昔の写真とか動画もたくさん保存されてるの。\n見てみる？もしかしたら、何か思い出すかもしれないわ。\nチューナー君、アルバム6860420を再生して。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>アルバム 6860420 再生シマス</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_3", "歌声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>*Every time we hide  \nInto shadow that can make us feel love \nEat the sorrow drink a cup of fear*</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>お姉ちゃん！お誕生日おめでとう！</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "これは……？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "お誕生日をお祝いしてくれてるの。覚えてる？\nAromaってば、本当にきれいな歌声……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……思い出せない……でも、この歌は…なんか懐かしい。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>あははは！お姉ちゃんおかしい！</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>ケーキを私に向かって投げるなんていい度胸ね……待ちなさい！あはは！</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "はは……楽しそう。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "小さい頃はあんなにヤンチャだったのに、今はこんなに人見知りだなんておかしいわよね。\nどう？何か思い出せそう？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……ううん……ごめんなさい。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "あ……で！でも！こ、こんなに楽しそうな思い出ばかりなら、早く思い出したいな……お姉ちゃん。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma……うぅ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あ……ダメね。落ち込んでる場合じゃないわ。\nあなたの言う通り、早く思い出せるように、お姉ちゃんもできる限りのことはするからね。\n体調も良さそうだし、アカデミーに復帰できるよう申請しておくわね。\nアカデミーにもたくさんお友達がいるのよ。\n記憶を思い出す手助けになるかもしれないわ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "アカデミー……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "1学期丸々休んじゃったけど、テストに合格すれば、前と同じクラスで勉強できるみたいだから。\nAromaは優等生だもの。きっと大丈夫よ！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "どうしたの？大丈夫？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あら、前にも会ったことあるけど、覚えてるかしら？\nお姉ちゃんの旦那のNoahよ。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "お……覚えてない。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "お気の毒に。\n忘れられた命の恩人さん。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "はは……いいんだよ。\nAromaちゃん、僕は君のお姉さんの夫であり、君の主治医でもあるNoah。\n住んでる場所も同じだから、何かあればいつでも頼ってね。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "はい……ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "騙されちゃダメよ。\nこの人は我が家で一番頼りにならないんだから。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "あはは……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ひどいなぁ……おいで、Aromaちゃん。\nこれを付けるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "この浮かんでる3つの装置は安定器だから、24時間つけっぱなしにする必要があるんだ。\n手術を終えたばかりで、嘔吐感やめまいなどの錯覚を起こすかもしれない。\n幻覚を見る可能性もあるけど、これをつけていれば、ある程度は抑制できるから。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "もちろん、これらの後遺症は、君の記憶喪失みたいに一時的なものに過ぎない。\n僕たちが君の大脳を完全に治してあげるからね。\nそうすれば、後遺症も徐々になくなって、記憶も戻ってくるからね。\n昔みたいに楽しく暮らせるようになるよ。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "この装置は、同時に脳波の検測も行ってくれるんだ。\nもし、何か異常を感知すれば、すぐに僕たちに知らせが届くようになってる。\nもし具合が悪くなったり、何かあった場合は、このボタンを押してね。\nそしたら、君の状況と居場所が分かるようになってるから。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma、何かあったら必ず私たちに話してね。\nお姉ちゃんたちはずっとあなたのそばにいるからね。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "分かった。\n本当にありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いいんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "唔……呃……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎麼了？很辛苦嗎？休息一下吧？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "沒關係……我把這段做完……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "九個月沒下床了，有點肌肉萎縮……好險只要復健就能復原。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……呼……做完了……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "來，喝點東西。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "謝謝……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "還記得嗎？三角果汁，妳以前最喜歡喝這個。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "想不起來嗎……？沒關係，妳能醒來姊姊就很開心了……\n啊！對了，來，妳的喇叭君。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_boot", "喇叭君開機"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "我的……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>Aroma 早安～早安～</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳從小就帶著的電子寵物，裡面有好多我們以前的照片跟影片喔。看看吧，也許對恢復記憶有幫助。\n喇叭君，播放相簿 6860420。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>相簿 6860420 投影開始。</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_3", "歌聲（Night Keepers - Bring the light）"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>*Every time we hide  \nInto shadow that can make us feel love \nEat the sorrow drink a cup of fear*</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>姊姊！生日快樂！</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "這是……？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳在幫我慶生喔，有印象嗎？Aroma 唱歌真的很好聽呢……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……沒什麼印象……不過這首歌很耳熟。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>哈哈哈！姊姊你好好笑！</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>居然敢拿蛋糕丟我，膽子不小啊……別跑！哈哈哈！</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哈哈……看起來好開心。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳小時候可皮的咧，長大卻變得那麼怕生。\n怎麼樣？有想起什麼了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……沒有……對不起。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "啊……不、不過如果過去我們都是那麼開心的話，我很希望可以快點想起來……姊姊。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊……不行不行，我怎麼能消沉呢？妳說得對，我們得快點幫妳想起來。\n妳身體恢復的狀況很棒，我可以跟學院申請復學，妳在班上也有好多朋友喔，跟他們待在一起一定有幫助的。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "學院……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "雖然已經超過一個學期了，不過只要考過升學測驗就可以接著之前的班級繼續讀。Aroma 是資優生，一定沒問題的！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "如何？狀況還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，雖然之前也見過了；記得他嗎？妳姊夫 Noah。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不……不記得。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "真可憐啊，被遺忘的救命恩人。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "哈哈……沒關係啦。\nAroma，我是 Noah，是妳的姊夫，也是主治醫生。我們就住在同一間房子，有什麼事都可以依靠我喔。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "別被他騙了……他是這個家最靠不住的傢伙。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "真過份吶……來，Aroma，戴上這個。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "這三個懸浮裝置是穩壓器，要 24 小時戴著。\n剛動完手術妳可能會產生錯覺性的嘔吐感或暈眩感，也可能有些許幻覺，這能有效抑制這些現象。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "當然這些後遺症都只是暫時的，就像妳的失憶一樣，我們把妳的大腦醫治得很完美，所以這些症狀都會隨著時間慢慢消失，妳的記憶一定也能漸漸恢復，再像以前一樣一起開心地生活吧。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "這個裝置也有腦波監測的功能，有任何異常它都會即時透過軟體通知我們。妳要是覺得不適或有什麼狀況只要按下這邊這個鈕，我們也能馬上知道妳的情況和位置。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，有什麼事一定要跟我們說，我們都在妳身邊。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "好，非常感謝。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不會。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "우……으……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "왜 그래? 많이 힘들어? 좀 쉴까?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "괜찮아……이것만 끝내고……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "9개월 동안이나 침대에서 내려오지 못했으니깐, 근육도 많이 수축돼있을 거야.... 재활 운동만 열심히 하면 회복할 수 있다고 하니 정말 다행이야.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응……휴우……끝났어……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "자, 마셔.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "고마워……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "기억나니? 이 삼각 주스, 네가 제일 좋아하던 건데.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "기억 안 나니……？괜찮아. 네가 깨어난 것만 해도 언니는 너무 기쁘니깐...아, 맞다! 자, 네 튜너군이야.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_boot", "튜너군 ON"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "내 튜너군……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>Aroma 굿모닝~ 굿모닝~</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "네가 어렸을 때부터 데리고 다닌 전자 애완 펫이야. 우리 옛날 사진이랑 영상도 많이 저장되어 있으니 함 볼래? 아마 기억이 회복되는 데에 도움이 될지도 몰라.\n튜너군, 앨범 6860420 재생해줘.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>앨범 6860420 빔 프로젝터 작업 중</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_3", "노랫 소리（Night Keepers - Bring the light）"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>*Every time we hide  \nInto shadow that can make us feel love \nEat the sorrow drink a cup of fear*</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>언니! 생일 축하해!</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "이건...?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "내 생일 축하 영상인데... 혹시 기억나? Aroma가 불러준 노래, 너무 좋았는데...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……그런 기억은 없는 것 같은데…… 그래도 이 노래... 귀에 익는 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>하하하하! 언니 너무 웃기다!</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>감히 내게 케이크를 던지다니...꽤 용기 있구나?.... 거기 서랏! 하하하!</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "하하하…… 엄청 즐거워 보인다.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "너 어렸을 때 얼마나 말을 안 들었는데!\n커가면서 조금 낯을 가리긴 했지만 말이야. 어때? 뭔가 떠오르는 거 없니?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……없어……미안\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "흑……만약 옛날에 우리가 저렇게 즐거웠다면... 나도 빨리 기억을 회복하고 싶어, 언니.....\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma……흐흑....\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "휴우……이러면 안 돼! 내가 침울해 있을 순 없지! 네 말이 맞아! 네가 빨리 기억을 되찾을 수 있도록 최선을 다할게. 그리고 네 몸 상태도 많이 회복되었으니깐 아카데미에 복학 신청서도 보낼 생각이야. 그곳에서 반 친구들이랑 함께 있다 보면 분명 기억 회복에 많은 도움이 될 거야.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "아카데미……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "이미 한 학기나 지나버렸지만, 그래도 월반 시험만 통과하면 예전에 같은 반 친구들과도 계속 함께 수업 들을 수 있을 거야. Aroma는 우등생이니깐, 분명 잘 해낼 수 있어!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응....\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "어때? 좀 나아진 것 같아?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "예전에도 만났었는데... 기억나? 네 형부 Noah야.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "아직……기억 못 하려나...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "불쌍하기도 하지... 생명의 은인인데 이렇게 잊혀지다니...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "하하……괜찮아.\nAroma, 내 이름은 Noah라고 한다. 네 형부이기도 하지. 그리고 네 주치의기도 해. 우린 같은 식구니깐, 무슨 일 있으면 언제든지 내게 말해주려무나.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "네.... 고마워요.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "저이한테 속으면 안 돼.... 우리 식구 중에 가장 의지가 안되는 녀석이거든.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "하하....\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "참 너무하네…… 자, Aroma. 이걸 쓰렴.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "이 3개의 부유 장치는 안정 장치니깐 24시간 때지 말고 항상 달고 있어야 해. 이제 막 수술이 끝난 참이라 착각성 구토나 어지럼증, 혹은 환각까지 보게 될 수도 있거든. 이 장치가 그러한 증상들을 억제시켜줄 거야.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "물론 그런 후유증도 네 기억 상실처럼 일시적인 현상일 뿐이니깐 너무 걱정하지 마. 네 수술도 매우 성공적으로 끝났으니깐 그러한 증상들도 시간이 지나면서 조금씩 사라질 거고 기억도 조금씩 되돌아올 거야. 그럼 다시 예전의 그 즐거웠던 시절로 돌아갈 수 있어.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "네……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "이 장치는 뇌파측정 기능도 가지고 있어. 만약 어떤 이상 생기면 즉시 어플을 통해 우리에게 알람이 올 거야. 만약 어딘가 불편하거나 무슨 상황이 생길 때 이 버튼을 누르면 즉시 우리에게 네 상태와 위치가 전송될 거야.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, 무슨 일 있으면 꼭 우리에게 말해줘. 우리가 항상 네 곁에 있을 거니깐.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응, 그럴게. \n고맙습니다.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니야. 고맙기는.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "唔……呃……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎麼了？很辛苦嗎？休息一下吧？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "沒關係……我把這段做完……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "九個月沒下床了，有點肌肉萎縮……好險只要復健就能復原。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……呼……做完了……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "來，喝點東西。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "謝謝……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "還記得嗎？三角果汁，妳以前最喜歡喝這個。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "想不起來嗎……？沒關係，妳能醒來姊姊就很開心了……\n啊！對了，來，妳的喇叭君。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_boot", "喇叭君開機"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "我的……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>Aroma 早安～早安～</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳從小就帶著的電子寵物，裡面有好多我們以前的照片跟影片喔。看看吧，也許對恢復記憶有幫助。\n喇叭君，播放相簿 6860420。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>相簿 6860420 投影開始。</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_3", "歌聲（Night Keepers - Bring the light）"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>*Every time we hide  \nInto shadow that can make us feel love \nEat the sorrow drink a cup of fear*</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>姊姊！生日快樂！</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "這是……？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳在幫我慶生喔，有印象嗎？Aroma 唱歌真的很好聽呢……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……沒什麼印象……不過這首歌很耳熟。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>哈哈哈！姊姊你好好笑！</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>居然敢拿蛋糕丟我，膽子不小啊……別跑！哈哈哈！</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哈哈……看起來好開心。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳小時候可皮的咧，長大卻變得那麼怕生。\n怎麼樣？有想起什麼了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……沒有……對不起。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "啊……不、不過如果過去我們都是那麼開心的話，我很希望可以快點想起來……姊姊。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊……不行不行，我怎麼能消沉呢？妳說得對，我們得快點幫妳想起來。\n妳身體恢復的狀況很棒，我可以跟學院申請復學，妳在班上也有好多朋友喔，跟他們待在一起一定有幫助的。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "學院……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "雖然已經超過一個學期了，不過只要考過升學測驗就可以接著之前的班級繼續讀。Aroma 是資優生，一定沒問題的！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "如何？狀況還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，雖然之前也見過了；記得他嗎？妳姊夫 Noah。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不……不記得。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "真可憐啊，被遺忘的救命恩人。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "哈哈……沒關係啦。\nAroma，我是 Noah，是妳的姊夫，也是主治醫生。我們就住在同一間房子，有什麼事都可以依靠我喔。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "別被他騙了……他是這個家最靠不住的傢伙。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "真過份吶……來，Aroma，戴上這個。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "這三個懸浮裝置是穩壓器，要 24 小時戴著。\n剛動完手術妳可能會產生錯覺性的嘔吐感或暈眩感，也可能有些許幻覺，這能有效抑制這些現象。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "當然這些後遺症都只是暫時的，就像妳的失憶一樣，我們把妳的大腦醫治得很完美，所以這些症狀都會隨著時間慢慢消失，妳的記憶一定也能漸漸恢復，再像以前一樣一起開心地生活吧。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "這個裝置也有腦波監測的功能，有任何異常它都會即時透過軟體通知我們。妳要是覺得不適或有什麼狀況只要按下這邊這個鈕，我們也能馬上知道妳的情況和位置。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，有什麼事一定要跟我們說，我們都在妳身邊。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "好，非常感謝。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不會。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "唔……呃……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎么了？很辛苦吗？休息一下吧？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "没关系……我把这段做完……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "九个月没下床了，有点肌肉萎缩……好险只要复健就能复原。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……呼……做完了……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "来，喝点东西。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "谢谢……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "还记得吗？三角果汁，妳以前最喜欢喝这个。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "想不起来吗……？没关系，妳能醒来姊姊就很开心了……\n啊！对了，来，妳的喇叭君。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_boot", "喇叭君开机"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "我的……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>Aroma 早安～早安～</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳从小就带着的电子宠物，里面有好多我们以前的照片跟影片喔。看看吧，也许对恢复记忆有帮助。\n喇叭君，播放相簿 6860420。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>相簿 6860420 投影开始。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_3", "歌声（Night Keepers - Bring the light）"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>*Every time we hide\nInto shadow that can make us feel love\nEat the sorrow drink a cup of fear*</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>姊姊！生日快乐！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "这是……？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳在帮我庆生喔，有印象吗？ Aroma 唱歌真的很好听呢……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……没什么印象……不过这首歌很耳熟。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Aroma]"], "content": "<i>哈哈哈！姊姊你好好笑！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>居然敢拿蛋糕丢我，胆子不小啊……别跑！哈哈哈！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哈哈……看起来好开心。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳小时候可皮的咧，长大却变得那么怕生。\n怎么样？有想起什么了吗？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……没有……对不起。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "啊……不、不过如果过去我们都是那么开心的话，我很希望可以快点想起来……姊姊。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma……呜……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊……不行不行，我怎么能消沉呢？妳說得对，我们得快点帮妳想起来。\n妳身体恢复的状况很棒，我可以跟学院申请复学，妳在班上也有好多朋友喔，跟他们待在一起一定有帮助的。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "学院……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "虽然已经超过一个学期了，不过只要考过升学测验就可以接着之前的班级继续读。 Aroma 是资优生，一定没问题的！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "如何？状况还好吗？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，虽然之前也见过了；记得他吗？妳姊夫 Noah。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不……不记得。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "真可怜啊，被遗忘的救命恩人。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "哈哈……没关系啦。\nAroma，我是 Noah，是妳的姊夫，也是主治医生。我们就住在同一间房子，有什么事都可以依靠我喔。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……谢谢。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "别被他骗了……他是这个家最靠不住的家伙。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "真过份呐……来，Aroma，戴上这个。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "这三个悬浮装置是稳压器，要 24 小时戴着。\n刚动完手术妳可能会产生错觉性的呕吐感或晕眩感，也可能有些许幻觉，这能有效抑制这些现象。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "当然这些后遗症都只是暂时的，就像妳的失忆一样，我们把妳的大脑医治得很完美，所以这些症状都会随着时间慢慢消失，妳的记忆一定也能渐渐恢复，再像以前一样一起开心地生活吧。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "这个装置也有脑波监测的功能，有任何异常它都会即时透过软体通知我们。妳要是觉得不适或有什么状况只要按下这边这个钮，我们也能马上知道妳的情况和位置。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，有什么事一定要跟我们说，我们都在妳身边。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "好，非常感谢。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不会。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}